query:
SELECT 
	Users.UserName 
	, Teams.TeamName

	, COUNT(Calls.Call_ID) AS n_calls
	, SUM(Calls.Duration)/60.0 AS min_calls
	, COUNT(Calls.Call_ID) + SUM(Calls.Duration)/60.0 AS cpm

FROM Users 
	LEFT OUTER JOIN Calls ON Calls.User_ID = Users.User_ID AND Calls.Organization_ID = 1
	LEFT OUTER JOIN Teams ON Teams.Team_ID = Calls.Team_ID

WHERE (1=1)
	AND Calls.CallDate = '20161130'
	AND Calls.Excluded = 0
	AND Users.Organization_ID = 1

GROUP BY UserName, TeamName 
ORDER BY cpm DESC
